<collectingCountry box="[597,672,1528,1554]" name="Brazil" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. This collection no longer exists and the 
<typeStatus box="[1149,1200,1528,1554]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">type</typeStatus>
is presumed lost, as also noted by 
<bibRefCitation author="Raven" box="[314,478,1568,1594]" pageId="2" pageNumber="20" refString="Raven, R. J. (1985) The spider infraorder Mygalomorphae (Araneae): cladistics and systematics. Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History, 182, 1 - 180." type="journal article" year="1985">
